Interface MapTransformerService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MapTransformerServiceImpl

    public MapTransformerService

    Service for transforming map.

    Service expand flattened map and vice versa.

    See Also:
    class MapTransformerServiceImpl

    • Method Detail

      • flattenMap

        @NotNull
java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> flattenMap(@NotNull
                                                                     java.util.Map<java.lang.String,? extends java.lang.Object> mapToFlatten)

        Flatten json data in map format.

        For example if there is such flatten map entry { 1 : { 2 : 4 } } it should return { 1.2 : 4 }.

        Parameters:
        mapToFlatten - expanded json data.
        Returns:
        Flattened expanded map.

      • expandToMapObjects

        @NotNull
java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> expandToMapObjects(@NotNull
                                                                             java.util.Map<java.lang.String,? extends java.lang.Object> flattenMap)

        Expand flattened map to MutableMap.

        For example if there is such flatten map entry { 1.2 : 4 } it should return { 1 : { 2 : 4 } }.

        Parameters:
        flattenMap - flattened json data.
        Returns:
        Expanded flattened map.
